 with his parents and two of his minor siblings, one of them a toddler, when the family homes were bombed. His uncle, who was wounded in the attack, died of his wounds on 22 November 2019. His aunt and two of his minor cousins were wounded along with 8 other people, 7 of them minors, were wounded.  [&lt;a text="" small="" href="https://www.btselem.org/gaza_strip/20191222_air_force_kills_14_civilians_in_gaza" target="_blank"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Salem Rasmi Salem a-Sawarkah&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;2-year-old resident of Deir al-Balah, killed on November 14, 2019, in Deir al-Balah,  by a bomb fired from an aircraft. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities.  Additional information: Killed along with his parents and two of his minor siblings, one of them a toddler, when the family homes were bombed. His uncle, who was wounded in the attack, died of his wounds on 22 November 2019. His aunt and two of his minor cousins were wounded along with 8 other people, 7 of them minors, were wounded.  [&lt;a text="" small="" href="https://www.btselem.org/gaza_strip/20191222_air_force_kills_14_civilians_in_gaza" target="_blank"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;May&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Maria Ahmad Ramadan al-Ghazali&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;Under 1 year old resident of Beit Lahiya, North Gaza District, killed on May 5, 2019, in Beit Lahiya, North Gaza District,  by a missile fired from an aircraft. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities.  Additional information: Three-month-old baby girl. Killed together with both her parents and three members of the Abu al-Jidyan family, one a minor, when their apartments, which border one another, were bombed in the a-Sheikh Zayed Tower.  [&lt;a text="" small="" href="https://www.btselem.org/gaza_strip/20190612_targeting_inhabited_gazan_homes" target="_blank"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h5 class="text-h5 fs-20 mt-5 mb-1"&gt;2018&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;December&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Ahmad Yasser Sabri Abu 'Abed&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;4 year old resident of Khan Yunis, injured on December 7, 2018, near the Gaza perimeter fence in the area of Khuza'ah, Khan Yunis District,  live ammunition, and died on December 11, 2018. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities.  Additional information: Injured in the head and upper body by shrapnel from Israeli security forces’ gunfire during the Return Protests near the Gaza perimeter fence, north of the town of Khuza’ah; thousands took part in the protests. At the protest, some demonstrators torched tires and threw stones at Israeli security forces stationed on the other side of the fence. Remained in a coma after his injury. His father was injured in the hand by shrapnel. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;August&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Bayan Muhammad Kamel Abu Khamash&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;1-year-old resident of Deir al-Balah, killed on August 9, 2018, in Deir al-Balah, by shelling fired from an aircraft. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities.  Additional information: Killed with her mother, who was in advanced stages of pregnancy, while they were asleep at home, by a bomb that penetrated their home without exploding. Her father was injured.  [&lt;a text="" small="" href="https://www.btselem.org/gaza_strip/20180917_bombing_of_abu_khamash_home_in_deir_al_balah" target="_blank"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h5 class="text-h5 fs-20 mt-5 mb-1"&gt;2015&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;October&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Rahaf Yihya Sa'di Hassan&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;3 year old resident of Gaza city, Gaza District, killed on October 11, 2015, in Gaza City, Gaza District,  by a missile fired from an aircraft. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities.  Additional information: Killed along with her mother when their home was bombed.  [&lt;a text="" small="" href="http://www.btselem.org/gaza_strip/20151022_bombing_of_hassan_family_home_gaza" target="_blank"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h5 class="text-h5 fs-20 mt-5 mb-1"&gt;2014&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;August&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Zeinah Bilal Sabri Abu Taqiyah&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;1-year-old resident of Gaza city, Gaza District, killed on August 24, 2014, in Gaza City, Gaza District,  by a missile fired from an aircraft. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities.  Additional information: Killed seated in a swing at the entrance to her home. A 16-year-old boy was killed on the porch of the neighboring house. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="mt-2"&gt;&lt;span class="v-chip v-chip--outlined theme--light v-size--x-small rounded-0 rounded-0--text" absolute=""&gt;&lt;span class="v-chip__content"&gt; Military operation: Protective Edge &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;'Abdallah Hayel Shehdeh Abu Dahruj&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;3 year old resident of a-Zawaydah, Deir al-Balah District, injured on August 22, 2014, in  Deir al-Balah, by gunfire fired from an aircraft, and died on August 23, 2014. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities.  Additional information: Killed with his parents and brother when their home and that of his grandfather were bombed. His father’s aunt, who lived in a nearby home, was also killed. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="mt-2"&gt;&lt;span class="v-chip v-chip--outlined theme--light v-size--x-small rounded-0 rounded-0--text" absolute=""&gt;&lt;span class="v-chip__content"&gt; Military operation: Protective Edge &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Hadi Hayel Shehdeh Abu Dahruj&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;1-year-old resident of a-Zawaydah, Deir al-Balah District, injured on August 22, 2014, in  Deir al-Balah, by gunfire fired from an aircraft, and died on August 23, 2014. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities.  Additional information: Killed with his parents and brother when their home and that of his grandfather were bombed. His father’s aunt, who lived in a nearby home, was also killed. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="mt-2"&gt;&lt;span class="v-chip v-chip--outlined theme--light v-size--x-small rounded-0 rounded-0--text" absolute=""&gt;&lt;span class="v-chip__content"&gt; Military operation: Protective Edge &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&