ah, injured on December 28, 2008, in Rafah,  by a missile, and died on December 29, 2008. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities.  Additional information: Killed with his two brothers while they were at home. Other members of the family were wounded and the house destroyed. Several hours earlier, armed persons had fired rockets from the area.  [&lt;a text="" small="" href="http://www.btselem.org/testimonies/20081228_three_children_killed_in_bombing_of_al_absi_home" target="_blank"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;div class="mt-2"&gt;&lt;span class="v-chip v-chip--outlined theme--light v-size--x-small rounded-0 rounded-0--text" absolute=""&gt;&lt;span class="v-chip__content"&gt; Military operation: Cast Lead &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Ahmad Riyad Muhammad a-Sinwar&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;3 year old resident of Gaza city, Gaza District, killed on December 27, 2008, in Gaza City, Gaza District,  by a missile fired from a helicopter. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities.  Additional information: Killed at home when a missile was fired at a Civil Defense building.  [&lt;a text="" small="" href="http://www.btselem.org/testimonies/20081231_3_year_old_ahmad_a_sinwar_killed_in_gaza_bombing" target="_blank"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;div class="mt-2"&gt;&lt;span class="v-chip v-chip--outlined theme--light v-size--x-small rounded-0 rounded-0--text" absolute=""&gt;&lt;span class="v-chip__content"&gt; Military operation: Cast Lead &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Tamer Hassan 'Ali al-Akhras&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;5 year old resident of Gaza city, Gaza District, killed on December 27, 2008, in Gaza City, Gaza District, by shelling fired from a fighter jet. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities.  Additional information: Killed while on his way home. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="mt-2"&gt;&lt;span class="v-chip v-chip--outlined theme--light v-size--x-small rounded-0 rounded-0--text" absolute=""&gt;&lt;span class="v-chip__content"&gt; Military operation: Cast Lead &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;April&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Hanaa Ahmad 'Eid Abu Me'teq&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;2-year-old resident of Beit Hanun, North Gaza District, killed on April 28, 2008, in  Beit Hanoun, North Gaza District,  by a missile fired from a helicopter. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed with her mother and three siblings while eating breakfast in the yard of their house.  [&lt;a text="" small="" href="http://www.btselem.org/press_releases/20080509" target="_blank"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Mus'ad Ahmad 'Eid Abu Me'teq&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;Under 1 year old resident of Beit Hanun, North Gaza District, killed on April 28, 2008, in  Beit Hanoun, North Gaza District,  by a missile fired from a helicopter. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed with his mother and three siblings while eating breakfast in the yard of their house.  [&lt;a text="" small="" href="http://www.btselem.org/press_releases/20080509" target="_blank"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Ruwaydah Ahmad 'Eid Abu Me'teq&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;5 year old resident of Beit Hanun, North Gaza District, killed on April 28, 2008, in  Beit Hanoun, North Gaza District,  by a missile fired from a helicopter. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed with her mother and three siblings while eating breakfast in the yard of their house.  [&lt;a text="" small="" href="http://www.btselem.org/press_releases/20080509" target="_blank"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt