div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Salsabil Majed Muhammad Abu Jalhum&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;2-year-old resident of Jabalya R.C., North Gaza District, killed on March 1, 2008, next to Jabalya, North Gaza District,  by a missile fired from a helicopter. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed while at home with her family during an incursion into the area. Three of her brothers were injured. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;February&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Muhammad Naser 'Abd al-'Aziz al-Bura'i&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;Under 1 year old resident of Gaza city, Gaza District, killed on February 27, 2008, in  Gaza City, Gaza District,  by a missile fired from a helicopter. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Six-month old infant. He was killed while sleeping in his bed when the ceiling collapsed on him as a result of the bombing of the Interior Ministry building.  [&lt;a text="" small="" href="http://www.btselem.org/testimonies/20080227_baby_killed_in_gaza_bombing_witness_muhammad_al_buri" target="_blank"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h5 class="text-h5 fs-20 mt-5 mb-1"&gt;2006&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;November&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Maram Ramez Ma'sud al-'Athamneh&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;3 year old resident of Beit Hanun, North Gaza District, killed on November 8, 2006, in Beit Hanoun, North Gaza District,  by a shell fired from a tank. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed while inside her home when Israeli artillery shells struck a residential neighborhood in Beit Hanun, killing 19 civilians, including 7 minors, and wounding some 40 others.  [&lt;a text="" small="" href="http://www.btselem.org/firearms/20061108_war_crime_in_beit_hanun" target="_blank"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Maysaa Ramez Ma'sud al-'Athamneh&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;Under 1 year old resident of Beit Hanun, North Gaza District, killed on November 8, 2006, in Beit Hanoun, North Gaza District,  by a shell fired from a tank. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed while inside her home when Israeli artillery shells struck a residential neighborhood in Beit Hanun, killing 19 civilians, including 7 minors, and wounding some 40 others.  [&lt;a text="" small="" href="http://www.btselem.org/firearms/20061108_war_crime_in_beit_hanun" target="_blank"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Baraa Riyad Muhammad Fayad&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;3 year old resident of Beit Hanun, North Gaza District, killed on November 2, 2006, in Beit Hanoun, North Gaza District,  by a missile fired from a helicopter. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed in his sleep. Seven members of his family were injured. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;October&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Iman Ousamah Fadel al-Harazin&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;3 year old resident of Gaza city, Gaza District, killed on October 12, 2006, in Gaza City, Gaza District,  by a missile fired from a helicopter. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed while walking with her father near a house bombed by the IDF, on their way to the clinic. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;August&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Rajaa Salam 'Abd al-Karim Abu Sh'aban&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;2-year-old resident of Gaza city, Gaza District, killed on August 9, 2006, in Gaza City, Gaza District, by gunfire. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Fell off a slide and bumped her head when a missile fired by the IDF hit an orchard 100 meters from the house. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Shahd Saleh 'Omar Sheikh al-'Eid&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;Under 1 year old resident of Rafah, killed on August 3, 2006, in Rafah, . &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: A three-day-old baby who fell from her mother's arms when she fled from their home due to IDF gunfire during an IDF operation in the southern Gaza Strip. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;July&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Baraa Ahmad Hussein Habib&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;2-year-old resident of Gaza city, Gaza District, killed on July 26, 2006, in  Gaza City, Gaza District,  by a missile fired from a helicopter. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed from gunfire aimed at a group of armed Palestinians, while standing next to her home. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Maria Samir 'Ata 'Okal&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;5 year old resident of Jabalya, North Gaza District, killed on July 26, 2006, in  Jabalya, North Gaza District,  by a shell fired from a tank. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed with her mother and sister while sitting in their yard. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Shahd Samir 'Ata 'Okal&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;Under 1 year old resident of Jabalya, North Gaza District, killed on July 26, 2006, in  Jabalya, North Gaza District,  by a shell fired from a tank. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed with her mother and sister while sitting in their yard. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Nasrallah Nabil Muhammad Abu Selmiyeh&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;5 year old resident of Gaza city, Gaza District, killed on July 12, 2006, in Gaza City, Gaza District,  by a missile fired from a fighter jet during the course of a targeted killing. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Nine members of the Abu Selmiyeh family, parents and 7 of their children, all minors, were killed by missile-fire aimed at their house. According to the IDF, senior Hamas-members were hiding in the house  [&lt;a text="" small="" href="http://www.btselem.org/firearms/20060712_family_killed_in_gaza_shelling" target="_blank"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Rawan Farid Sha'ban Hajjaj&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;5 year old resident of Gaza city, Gaza District, killed on July 8, 2006, in Gaza City, Gaza District, by gunfire. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed with his mom and brother during "Operation Summer Rains" when they were in their house. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;June&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Majzarah Sha'ban 'Abd al-Qader Ahmad&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;Under 1 year old resident of Khan Yunis, killed on June 21, 2006, in Khan Yunis,  by a missile fired from a helicopter during the course of a targeted killing. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Died 12 hours after birth, as a result of shrapnel that penetrated to the mother's womb.  [&lt;a text="" small="" href="http://www.btselem.org/firearms/20060622_gaza_missiles" target="_blank"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Khaled Nidal 'Abd al-Karim Wahbah&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;1-year-old resident of Rafah R.C., Rafah District, injured on June 21, 2006, in Khan Yunis,  by a missile fired from a helicopter during the course of a targeted killing, and died on July 10, 2006. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed at home by missile fire aimed at wanted persons riding in a vehicle on the street nearby.  [&lt;a text="" small="" href="http://www.btselem.org/firearms/20060622_gaza_missiles" target="_blank"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Samia Mahmoud Ziad a-Sharif&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;5 year old resident of Gaza city, Gaza District, killed on June 20, 2006, in Gaza City, Gaza District,  by a missile fired from a helicopter during the course of a targeted killing. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed while was on her way to the grocery store besidde her house. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Muhammad Jamal 'Abed Rouqah&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;4 year old resident of Gaza city, Gaza District, killed on June 20, 2006, in Gaza City, Gaza District,  by a missile fired from a helicopter during the course of a targeted killing. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed while was on his way to the grocery store besidde his house. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h5 class="text-h5 fs-20 mt-5 mb-1"&gt;2004&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;October&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Luai Ayman Muhammad a-Najar&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;4 year old resident of Khan Yunis, killed on October 4, 2004, in Khan Yunis,  by a shell fired from a tank. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed near his house when IDF tanks entered the a-Sh'auth area. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;July&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Samar 'Omar Hassan Fujo&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;3 year old resident of Rafah, injured on July 8, 2004, in Rafah, by gunfire, and died on July 18, 2004. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed when she was shot in the head while standing near her house in the Tal-Zo'arub neighborhood. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;May&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Rawan Muhammad Sa'id Abu Zeid&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;4 year old resident of Rafah, killed on May 22, 2004, in Rafah, by gunfire. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed on her way to the store during the IDF's incursion into Rafah. Shot in the head and neck. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h5 class="text-h5 fs-20 mt-5 mb-1"&gt;2003&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;October&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Mustafa 'Abd al-Qader Isma'il al-Badrasawi&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;1-year-old resident of Khan Yunis, injured on October 2, 2003, in Khan Yunis,  by a shell fired from a tank, and died on October 4, 2003. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed while on the roof of his house, by gunfire coming from the area of the Ganei Tal settlement. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;July&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Mahmoud Jawdat Sharif Kabha&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;3 year old resident of Barta'a a-Sharqiya, Jenin District, killed on July 25, 2003, at the checkpoint in the area of Barta'ah a-Sharqiyah, Jenin District, by gunfire. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed by an army tank that mistakenly fired at the car he was in with his family, while they were waiting to cross a checkpoint. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;June&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Afnan Yasser Muhammad Taha&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;Under 1 year old resident of al-Bureij R.C., Deir al-Balah District, killed on June 12, 2003, in Gaza City, Gaza District,  by a missile fired from a helicopter during the course of a targeted killing. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Infant daughter of Yasser Taha, killed with her mother in the assassination attack on her father. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;May&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;'Alian Bashiti&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;1-year-old resident of Khan Yunis R.C., Khan Yunis District, killed on May 7, 2003, in  Khan Yunis R.C., Khan Yunis District, by gunfire. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed during an IDF incursion into Khan Yunis &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Amir Ahmad Muhammad 'Ayad&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;2-year-old resident of Gaza city, Gaza District, killed on May 1, 2003, in Gaza City, Gaza District, by gunfire. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed during an IDF incursion into Gaza city. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;March&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Ilham Ziad Hassan al-'Assar&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;4 year old resident of a-Nuseirat Camp, Deir al-Balah District, killed on March 17, 2003, in  a-Nuseirat R.C., Deir al-Balah District, by gunfire. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed in an IDF operation in the camp. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h5 class="text-h5 fs-20 mt-5 mb-1"&gt;2002&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;November&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Humad al-Masri&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;2-year-old resident of Rafah R.C., Rafah District, killed on November 13, 2002, in Rafah R.C., Rafah District, by gunfire. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.   &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Nafez Mash'al&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;2-year-old resident of Rafah, killed on November 11, 2002, in Rafah, by gunfire. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.   &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;October&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Tawfiq Husam Hafez Bariqi&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;2-year-old resident of Rafah, killed on October 13, 2002, in Rafah, by house demolition. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed when his house was collapsed when the IDF blew up an adjacent house that had a tunnel. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;September&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Gharam Muhammad Ibrahim Man'a&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;1-year-old resident of a-Dhahiriyah, Hebron District, killed on September 26, 2002, in Hebron,  by a teargas canister. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed by a grenade fired during an IDF operation to enforce curfew. &lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12"&gt;&lt;h6 class="fw-400 fs-16 mb-3"&gt;July&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Muhammad Mahmoud al-Huti&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;3 year old resident of Gaza city, Gaza District, killed on July 22, 2002, in Gaza City, Gaza District,  by a bomb fired from a fighter jet during the course of a targeted killing. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed in his sleep when a one-ton bomb was dropped on the building in which he was in.  [&lt;a text="" small="" href="http://www.btselem.org/firearms/20070918_shahadah_assassination_appeal" target="_blank"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Subhi Mahmoud al-Huti&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;5 year old resident of Gaza city, Gaza District, killed on July 22, 2002, in Gaza City, Gaza District,  by a bomb fired from a fighter jet during the course of a targeted killing. &lt;!----&gt; Did not participate in hostilities when killed.  Additional information: Killed in his sleep when a one-ton bomb was dropped on the building in which he was in.  [&lt;a text="" small="" href="http://www.btselem.org/firearms/20070918_shahadah_assassination_appeal" target="_blank"&gt;More Info&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;!----&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;!----&gt;&lt;div class="col-12 col-md-6"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto mb-3 h-100 v-card v-sheet v-sheet--outlined theme--light" style="height: 100%;"&gt;&lt;div tabindex="-1" class="v-list-item v-list-item--three-line theme--light"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__content"&gt;&lt;div class="v-list-item__title headline fs-17 text--dark-blue mb-2"&gt;Ayman Raed Matar&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="fs-14 lh-19 mb-0"&gt;2-year-o